import React,{useContext} from 'react' import flightContent from "../context/FlightContext"; import '../styles/FetchBooking.css' const FetchBooking = () => { const content = useContext(flightContent) const {fetchbooking} = content return (
Your trip summary
{fetchbooking.map((element)=>{ return
BOOKING ID
CLASS
BOOKING STATUS
{element.bookingid}
ECONOMY
BOOKING CONFIRMED
Outbound flight
{element.departuredate}
{element.destinationdate}
{element.departuretime}
{element.departurecode}
{element.destinationtime}
{element.destinationcode}
Opearted by {element.flightname}
{element.triptype === 'Return'?
Inbound flight
{element.rdeparturedate}
{element.rdestinationdate}
{element.rdeparturetime}
{element.rdeparturecode}
{element.rdestinationtime}
{element.rdestinationcode}
Opearted by {element.rflightname}
: <> }
} ) }
{fetchbooking.map((element)=>{ return <>
Payment Details
Base fare
{element.totalprice}
Amount Paid
{element.totalprice}
})}
{/*
Total trip price:
{adultCounter?<>{adultCounter} Adult:''}{childCounter?<>+{childCounter}Child:''}{infantCounter?<>+{infantCounter}Infant:''}
{tripValue === 'Return'?(passCount-infantCounter)*(tripFlights[0].economyprice+tripFlights[1].economyprice):(passCount-infantCounter)*(tripFlights[0].economyprice)}
*/}
) } export default FetchBooking
